OL,3,C'Missed chances' to save newborn who
OL,4,Cdied after six hours
OL,6,FThe mother of a baby who died in
OL,7,Fhospital six hours after his birth,
OL,8,Fhas said a Bradford hospital 'failed'
OL,9,Fher.
OL,11,FEllen Standing gave birth to Hugo at
OL,12,FBradford Infirmary, where he was only
OL,13,Falive long enough to be held by his
OL,14,Fmum and brothers.
OL,16,FHe died from a severe brain injury,
OL,17,Fcaused by a lack of oxygen from a
OL,18,Fplacenta abruption last August.
OL,20,FMs Standing says there were multiple
OL,21,Fchances to save his life.
