OL,3,C'Missed chances' to save newborn who
OL,4,Cdied after six hours
OL,6,FShe said: "Well I never thought i'd
OL,7,Fhave to leave a hospital without my
OL,8,Fbaby. I don't want any other mum to go
OL,9,Fthrough what i went through."
OL,11,FAfter Hugo's death, Ms Standing
OL,12,Freceived a report highlighting
OL,13,Ffailures in her care that could have
OL,14,Fbeen prevented.
OL,16,FA report issued soon after by the
OL,17,Fhospital says heart monitoring was not
OL,18,Fstarted soon enough and urgent blood
OL,19,Ftests were delayed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
