OL,3,C'Missed chances' to save newborn who
OL,4,Cdied after six hours
OL,6,FIt said monitors were take off too
OL,7,Fearly and 'continuous foetal heart
OL,8,Fmonitoring was not performed'. When
OL,9,Fthe monitoring was recommenced in
OL,10,Ftheatre the foetal heart appeared to
OL,11,Fbe bradycardic (low).
OL,13,FThere was also a "missed opportunity"
OL,14,Fto have a full neonatal team available
OL,15,Fbefore the Caesarean section took
OL,16,Fplace.
OL,18,FMs Standing was deemed a high risk
OL,19,Fpatient, due to her Type 2 Diabetes,
OL,20,Fsmoking and hypertension, which are
OL,21,Frisk factors for placental abruption.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
