OL,3,C'Missed chances' to save newborn who
OL,4,Cdied after six hours
OL,6,FShe was dismissed by the hospital when
OL,7,Fshe raised concerns of 'painful and
OL,8,Fright contractions' which were passed
OL,9,Foff as Braxton Hicks pains.
OL,11,FMs Standing reflected on how difficult
OL,12,Fit was to hear other babies being born
OL,13,Fand seeing other mums leaving the
OL,14,Fhospital with their babies.
OL,16,FShe said: "It's not a nice thing to
OL,17,Fdo."
OL,19,FA number of key learning points were
OL,20,Fconsidered by the hospital after Ms
OL,21,FStanding's birth.
