OL,3,C'Missed chances' to save newborn who
OL,4,Cdied after six hours
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Bradford Teaching
OL,7,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust said:
OL,8,F"We would like to express our sincere
OL,9,Fcondolences to the family for their
OL,10,Fsad loss.
OL,12,F"We have shared the findings of a
OL,13,Freview following Hugo's death with
OL,14,FEllen, but if she wishes to discuss
OL,15,Fthe contents of this report or has any
OL,16,Funanswered questions about her care,
OL,17,Fwe urge her to contact us directly
OL,18,Feither via the Maternity team or our
OL,19,FPatient Experience team."
