OL,3,C'Missed chances' to save newborn who
OL,4,Cdied after six hours
OL,6,FThe incident follows changes made in
OL,7,Fthe hospital's neonatal department
OL,8,Fafter concerns in previous years about
OL,9,Fthe number of deaths.
OL,11,FMP Naz Shah, has spoken about the
OL,12,Fstandard of care on the neonatal unit,
OL,13,Fclaiming basic hygiene at the hospital
OL,14,Fwas not being met.
OL,16,FA recent report found neonatal deaths
OL,17,Fat Bradford's hospital was three times
OL,18,Fabove the national target amount.
